{
  "stem": "16571.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I was saying the worst incident which happened to me, besides being starved, and starving of hunger, and all the rest of it, one morning, there was a commotion going on.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And like, I'd just managed to drag myself through the door, and I saw-- because we didn't have plates, or soup-- soup plates, or anything, we just had tins with a little handle, like painters have, and I saw these people [? running ?] in with this liquid.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went and got my tin, and I went out and I got this liquid-- this soup.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What it was, I don't even know what it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Suddenly, they've-- they heard the commotion, the kapos, and they come into the block and they started beating people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think about three or four got killed from beating over the heads.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I put my tin [BACKROUND NOISE] between two bunks on the floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I could-- I was thin, I was little.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I could climb under the bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I went into-- into my bunk and I pretended I was asleep.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was shuddering, I was tittering.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If they found-- If they would have just asked me, where's my tin, I would have had to say, oh, here it is.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I wouldn't have had enough sense to say, I don't know, somebody stole it or something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Luckily for me, I wouldn't be here today to tell the tale, they-- they thought I was asleep.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They never bothered me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when I think about that, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- I just shudder.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that is the worst thing which happened to me whist in Belsen.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
